data.description: This bright and sprawling 950+ square foot one bedroom residence at 2601 Parkway is not to be missed! This coveted unit used to be the developer’s model home for the building. The living and dining areas are generously proportioned and boost gleaming parquet wood floor and a wall of windows which fill the home with an abundance of natural light. The kitchen features beautiful shaker style wood cabinets, sleek countertops, and designer fixtures. The bedroom is oversized and offers ample closet space. The updated bathroom showcases ceramic tiles, chrome fixtures, and a ceramic sink with storage vanity.. Condo Fees include water & sewer, a convenient shuttle service, state-of-the-art fitness center, and 24 hour lobby attendant. Perfectly located across from The Art Museum and Fairmount Park, this beautiful pet-friendly residence is close to Kelly Drive, Boat House Row, Whole Foods Market, The Barnes, great restaurants, and convenient transportation
